suite.doc: This test suite covers the following test scenarios for trivago magazine (https://magazine.trivago.com/): 1. Search for “Texas” using the search functionality a. Verify that the displayed number of search results is correct 2. From the displayed results open “Mom Knows Best: Family Vacations in Texas” a. Verify that the list of “Featured hotels and resorts” displays all hotels featured in the article, b. Verify that there are no broken links in the article
